long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With this free AI face swapper, you can easily and quickly swap two faces in images or videos. It use AI technology to merge them together and transfer one facial feature to another to create realistic images and videos. 

What is AI face swap?

A face swap tool uses AI algorithms to transform one face into another by blending facial features and creating transition from one face to another. This kind of face swapper is used in entertainment, such as movies and videos, and also used for fun.

Key features:

Advanced AI technology: Cutting-edge AI delivers incredibly realistic and convincing morphing effects.
Face Swapping with Characters: Merge your facial features with legendary characters to become anyone you want.
Boost Your Social Media with Face Swap AI: Combine your face with celebrities, try gender swaps, or experiment with face swaps to boost likes, shares, and smiles on your social media.
Change Faces: Digitally swap faces between individuals in photos or videos. It detects and replaces faces seamlessly, allowing you to create entertaining or unique images. 
Face Detection: Identifies and isolates faces in the images or video.
Face Matching: Analyzes the facial features and expressions to ensure a natural fit for the swap video and photos.
Seamless Combination: The faces are swapped and blended into the new context, adjusting for size, orientation, and lighting to look realistic.
Smart Adjustments: Adjust elements like face size, position, and blend to perfect the effect.

How to use this tool to swap face photos and videos:
It’s very easy to use, only two steps:
Step 1 Right click on the photos or videos with the faces you want to swap 
Step 2 Then click on the button to start face swapping process and then you will get the high resolution face swapped results.
